        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-7 text-center">
                <h2 class="section-title text-center mb-5">Clients Review</h2>

                <div class="owl-single owl-carousel no-nav">
                    <div class="testimonial mx-auto">
                        <figure class="img-wrap">
                            <img src="~/images/person_3.jpg" alt="Image" class="img-fluid">
                        </figure>
                        <h3 class="name">Ahmad</h3>
                        <blockquote>
                            <p>&ldquo;Thank you for the outstanding facilities and service during our trip. Everything was perfect, and we look forward to more destinations in the future..&rdquo;</p>
                        </blockquote>
                    </div>

                    <div class="testimonial mx-auto">
                        <figure class="img-wrap">
                            <img src="~/images/person_1.jpg" alt="Image" class="img-fluid">
                        </figure>
                        <h3 class="name">Jafar</h3>
                        <blockquote>
                            <p>&ldquo;We had a fantastic experience with your travel company. The facilities were top-notch, and your team's attention to detail was impressive. We can 't wait to book our next adventure with you..&rdquo;</p>
                        </blockquote>
                    </div>

                    <div class="testimonial mx-auto">
                        <figure class="img-wrap">
                            <img src="~/images/slider_3.jpg" alt="Image" class="img-fluid">
                        </figure>
                        <h3 class="name">Mr alax</h3>
                        <blockquote>
                            <p>&ldquo;Your travel company was great! Everything was awesome, and we'll definitely book with you again..&rdquo;</p>
                        </blockquote>
                    </div>

                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>